cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.SD (Sound): The paper focuses on voice synthesis and uses audio signals as input. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper uses natural language text as input and generates speech output. 
- cs.SD (Signal Processing): The paper uses signal processing techniques to extract rhythm and pitch information from audio signals. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses machine learning techniques to train the Mellotron model. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses AI techniques to generate expressive speech and singing voices.
